data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Located in a Golf Cart Beach Community off the Gulf Of Mexico, this one-story 3/2/2 Island home has a welcoming layout & kept well maintained. It offers a NEW ROOF, NEW AC, open floorplan, stainless steel appliances (frig conveys), wood burning fireplace, high ceilings, spacious kitchen & living area, Newer energy saving water-heater, fresh exterior paint, RV & Boat parking, nice natural lighting, remodeled walk-in shower, double sinks, garden tub, large primary closet, sky-light in guest bath, screened in patio with New fan/lights, & there is room for a POOL:) SELLER SAYS SELL.... BRING US AN OFFER!! No Showtime Please
